                  ></path></svg
                ></span
              >
              <div>
                <strong>High-Efficiency Systems</strong>
                <p>
                  Modern units cool so fast they don't run long enough for meaningful
                  dehumidification
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-card">
              <span class="icon-card__icon"
